===Rewards===
[[File:Item Winter Cheerizer.png|right|thumb|The "Winter Cheerizer" item.]]
The following rewards could be obtained from this event:

* Festive Starter Pack
** Available to everyone
** "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|Festive Starter Pack]]" bundle

* The First Gift
** Available to users who gifted one VRC+ subscription or Shop gift.<ref name="Gifts" group="note">Gifting shop items, avatars, world store listings and VRC+ subscriptions all count toward the tracker. </ref>
** "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|Tree-in-a-Box]]" Premium [[Special:MyLanguage/Emojis|emoji]]

* VRC+ Gifter
** Available to users who gifted one VRC+ subscription.<ref name="Gifts" group="note" />
** "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|VRC+ Gifter]]" bundle

* Holiday Legend
** Available to users who gifted five VRC+ subscriptions or Shop gifts.<ref name="Gifts" group="note" />
** "Wrapped Up!" [[Special:MyLanguage/Warp Effects|warp effect]]

* Community Spirit Reward
** Available to everyone after reaching the gifting goal of 200,000 gifts given.<ref name="Gifts" group="note" />
** "Winter Cheerizer" [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|item]]

* Keeper of the Spirit
** Available to users who claimed the "Festive Starter Pack", "The First Gift", "VRC+ Gifter", and "Holiday Legend" rewards.
** "Keeper of the Spirit" [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]]

